        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>prawn & pineapple panang curry</strong> over the <strong>edamame & jasmine rice</strong></p><p>Tear over the <strong>coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
